messages.content: It seems like you're testing something. How can I assist you further?
Got it, I'll remember the number 88765 for you.
You asked me to remember the number 88765.
Glad I could help! If you need anything else, feel free to ask.
Thank you! I'm here to assist you whenever you need.
from now on I want you to call me boss
Understood, Boss. Just let me know how I can help you.
and don't say "yes" or "no". I want you to respond with "Yes, Sir." and "No, Sir" understand?
Yes, Sir. I understand your request.
You're welcome, Boss. If you need further assistance, feel free to ask.
